  "parent_id": "2885492965",
  "children": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below is the example for How to write test case for injecting a dlt command and reading the delt logs in RFW"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step1: Make sure the TestBench.py has correct configuration ."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Path: Config\\Autosar\\integration-test\\Service.UTFManager.Aurix\\RFW_UTF\\Configuration"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Make sure COM port is as per the device manager port"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/9.%20RFW%20Test%20case%20to%20inject%20and%20read%20DLT%20log/image-2023-3-29_16-12-35.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/9. RFW Test case to inject and read DLT log/image-2023-3-29_16-12-35.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 2: In Test Suite Initialize use the key word launch dlt connector to connect to launch connection to DLT daemon ."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/9.%20RFW%20Test%20case%20to%20inject%20and%20read%20DLT%20log/image-2023-3-29_16-16-37.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/9. RFW Test case to inject and read DLT log/image-2023-3-29_16-16-37.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 3: To inject we need to use injection key word. Explained the format in below picture"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/9.%20RFW%20Test%20case%20to%20inject%20and%20read%20DLT%20log/image-2023-3-29_16-37-42.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/9. RFW Test case to inject and read DLT log/image-2023-3-29_16-37-42.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We can use searchstring and timeout in injection command to check the expected dlt log"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 4: Monitoring and Searching for a particular Dlt log"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "we need to use two key words, one to start monitor and another to search the logs"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Start Monitoring",
        "Search Logs <search_string> <timeout>"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/9.%20RFW%20Test%20case%20to%20inject%20and%20read%20DLT%20log/image-2023-3-29_16-47-42.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/9. RFW Test case to inject and read DLT log/image-2023-3-29_16-47-42.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 5: The output.xml in this path Config\\Autosar\\integration-test\\Service.UTFManager.Aurix\\RFW_UTF\\_Reports will have complete details on DLT logs"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/9.%20RFW%20Test%20case%20to%20inject%20and%20read%20DLT%20log/image-2023-3-29_17-37-26.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/9. RFW Test case to inject and read DLT log/image-2023-3-29_17-37-26.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "If the search string is found, the test case will pass, otherwise it will fail"
    }
  ],
